SpoonerPlacements.Note: Since the first caveman jumped off a cliff in a futile bid to get laid, man has dreamed of flight. The perfect freedom, the solitude, the silence. Well, now that dream is real. Only you're strapped into the love child of a super car and a space shuttle, there's 15 other grinning lunatics on every side of you, and all you can hear are explosions and screams. So quite a bit better, if anything. Lap race for the Rocket Voltic.
